Hi, if I switch trackers, do I need to re-setup my purchase postback? Or will it still work with another tracker?

Hi Nathaniel! If you switch trackers, you will need to re-setup your purchase postback with the new tracker. Each tracker has its own unique setup process, so it's important to follow the specific instructions for the new tracker you're using. Let me know if you need any help with the setup!
Are you certain? Won't S2S work regardless?

Switching trackers usually requires re-setting up your purchase postback because each tracker has its own unique setup and parameters. While S2S (server-to-server) postbacks can work across different platforms, the specific implementation details might vary. It's always best to follow the setup guide for your new tracker to ensure everything is configured correctly. If you need help with a specific tracker, let me know which one you're switching to, and I can provide more detailed guidance.
